description.narrative: UNICEF's technical and financial support to MoHSP for continues quality improvement of Maternal, Neonatal, and Child Health (MNCH) services, and the application of tools and standards developed with UNICEF technical support strengthened the child focus of the National Health Strategy 2021 to 2030, and contributed to improved quality of maternal, child and neonatal care and scaling up of essential maternal and child interventions. Approval of immunization communication strategy developed with UNICEF support provides an opportunity for improved equity focus of immunization services in 2020 and beyond. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:16/12/2019
